		<description><![CDATA[This week, Toby Bowers director of Bikechain joined the program.  Bikechain acts as a biking advocacy and outreach group.  Offering a fully equipped bike shop and bike professionals to help students learn to fix their own bikes. In our second feature, We meet with John Bennet, executive director of the Sierra Club of Canada.  John will talk to us about the BlackOutSpeakOut campaign that is currently underway which has a wide assortment of the biggest environmental NGO's in Canada blacking out their websites on June 4th to protest what he see's as a continuing war on environmentalism by the Federal government.]]></description>
